Anzeige *Hey Leute, 
War eine harte Trainingssession heute. Um genügend Power zu haben nehme ich während des Trainings 5g L-Arginin von @officialbodylab24 . Hilft meinem Herz-Kreislaufsystem auch heftigste Einheiten zu überstehen, unterstützt den EiweißStoffwechsel und die Fettverbrennung und gibt mir den heftigsten Pump 🔥!

Hol dir L-Arginin und andere Supplements bei @officialbodylab24 mit meinem Code AMIN33 und spare nochmals 33% 🤙🏾

#bodylap24 #bdlb24crew #officialbodylap24

node.text:
3 month transformation💪🏾!
I told you i’ll be back !
Left pic is from mai 2021, right pic is from today.
In between were only Blood, Toil, Tears and sweat and my greatest enemy was myself.

If you think you can't win the battle against yourself, let me help you. Together we will bring you to the top💪🏾

Hit the link in my bio 👆🏾 for a free call with me or my team and let’s talk about your goals 👊🏾

#transformation #transformationoftheday #dedication #believeinyourself

It is raining 🌧 ? No problem ! The training continues 💪🏾. Here are some exercises you can do with a barbell in the gym or at home. The legs are completely destroyed afterwards💪🏾

Save and go for it !

#legs #legworkout #noexcuses

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AMIN ELKACH | ONLINE COACH on August 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, biceps, beard, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
it's another year. time is running and we are getting older but more important is what we do with our time cause you can not stop it ,you can only make the best of it The last 5 years have gone by so fast with me. I would never have seen me where I am right now but I have big goals. I am very grateful and at the same time motivated to achieve more🙏🏾🤲🏾
This year I had again lows and highs but unfortunately more difficult and negative times than positive ones. I did fight very hard to defeat all these negative moments and I have made it💪🏾. Today I stand here again like a soldier and am ready to keep up what I started 🦾

Time is running . set yourself goals and make something out of it and don't forget to be happy because happiness is the most important thing in life 💯

Thank you very much for all your congratulations . it has touched me very much🥺 . Love you all ♥️

#thankyou #birthday #motivation

👉🏾CHEST WORKOUT 👈🏾

SAVE FOR LATER 🤙🏾

Thanks god I can train again 🙏🏾. Today I had a killer chest session .I am trying to be more creative with my training  and of course I train very careful. Feel free to increase the weight if you can . Today’s exercises are absolute destroyers . Give them a try 🤙🏾

🌪Incline triangle press  4x 20-15
🌪Stacked plate press.  4x 15-12
🌪Incline circle fly.  4x 15-12
🌪Flat dumbbell alternating bench press 4x 15-12
🌪Flat Dumbell Bench press 4x 15-12

Let’s go !

#chestday #chestworkout #chestgains #chesttraining #chestexercises

👉🏾Shoulder Session 👈🏾

SAVE FOR LATER 🔥 

My right arm is unfortunately still not really healthy, that’s why i can't train with much weight . Much weight is also not always important . You can stimulate the muscles in other ways. Today a few shoulder exercises that are extremely effective and help your delts to grow 💪🏾

4 x 15-12
30-40 sec rest between the sets 

Give them a try🤙🏾

#shoulderworkout #shoulders #shouldertraining #delts #homeworkout #workoutexercises
